      <h2 id="birthday">What is birthday clalendar?</h2>

      <p>Birthday calendar shows date-of-birth from the Contact app.</p>

      <p>To add a new birthday, please set the date-of-birth for the appropriate contact.</p>

      <ol>
         <li>Open Contact app</li>
         <li>Tap on "Add field"</li>
         <li>Tap on "Birthday"</li>
         <li>Set the Birthday</li>
      </ol>

